GROWTH and STRENGTH
1. Revenue and profits going up (are dividends increasing?)
2. Balance sheet
	- Assets vs Liabilities
	- Is debt long term or short term?
	- Current Assets vs Current Liabilities
3. Is this something I would buy/am I familiar with this company?

UNDERVALUED?
3. P/B ratio vs actual price
4. P/E ratio vs industry (calculate PEG also)
5. Temporary setback at bargain price? (bear market, oil prices falling, weakening dollar etc.)
6. Compared to the other companies is it undervalued?

6. Read the report on what management thinks of the company's future.
